  ],
  "difficulty": 1.5,
  "summary": "一开始想复杂了，不需要找规律什么的，实际上对于异或和，我们不关心中间具体都是什么数。把前 $n - 2$ 个数用<strong>随机数</strong>构造出来，构造的过程中记录奇数位和偶数位的异或和，然后用<strong>最后两个数</strong>把这两个异或和搞成相等的即可。",
  "link": "https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1722/G",
  "link_text": "Problem - 1722G - Codeforces",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
  "parent": null,
  "format": "logseq",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "给定一个正整数 $n$，请你找出一个长度为 $n$ 数组 $a$，满足数组是由互不相同的非负且小于 $2^{31}$ 的整数组成，并且该数组中奇数项上元素的异或和与偶数项上元素的异或和要相等。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "输入的第一行为一个整数 $t$ $(1 \\leq t \\leq 629)$，表示测试点的数量。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "接下来 $t$ 行，每行一个整数 $n$ $(3 \\leq n \\leq 2 \\times 10^5)$，表示数组的长度。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "保证所有测试点中 $n$ 的总和不超过 $2 \\times 10^5$。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于每个测试点，在一行中输出 $n$ 个不同的满足条件的整数。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果有多种答案，你可以输出任意一种。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "样例",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "输入",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "7\n8\n3\n4\n5\n6\n7\n9",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "4 2 1 5 0 6 7 3\n2 1 3\n2 1 3 0\n2 0 4 5 3\n4 1 2 12 3 8\n1 2 3 4 5 6 7\n8 2 3 7 4 0 5 6 9",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "在第一个测试点中，奇数项的异或和为 $4 \\oplus 1 \\oplus 0 \\oplus 7 = 2$；偶数项的异或和为 $2 \\oplus 5 \\oplus 6 \\oplus 3 = 2$。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tconst int MAX = (1ll << 31) - 1;\n\tvar ans = vector<int>();\n\n\tint ji = 0, ou = 0;\n\tvar se = set<int>();\n\tfa(i, 1, n - 2) {\n\t\tint x = MT::randint<int>(0, MAX);\n\t\twhile (se.count(x))x = MT::randint<int>(0, MAX);\n\t\tse.insert(x);\n\t\tans.pb(x);\n\t\tif (i & 1) ji ^= x;\n\t\telse ou ^= x;\n\t}\n\t// 用最后两个数进行修正，最后等于 MAX 或 ji ^ ou\n\tans.pb(ou ^ MAX), ans.pb(ji ^ MAX); \n\n\tcout << ans << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
